title: Talk About a Stranger [1952 - USA] noir mystery
description:
Talk About a Stranger (1952 - USA)

Drama / Film-Noir / Mystery
 
http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0045216/


A tightly-wound tale of suspicion and mob violence, made all the more forceful by the brilliant camera work of noir visionary John Alton. In this unsettling twist on The Boy Who Cried Wolf, young Billy Gray tries to convince his small town neighbours that a reclusive stranger has poisoned his dog, and may be a murderer in hiding.
